cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is about data augmentation for object detection, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a novel method for data augmentation, which involves balancing instance and class importance, indicating that it may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper uses deep learning models for object detection, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
